quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,30,Some femina oppidum gossiped governor's uxor est trying seduce eam servus! She est deeply in love eum! Nos vide she iit astray
  12,31,When she heard their gossip she invited them prepared them comfortable locus dedit each de them knife She tunc dictus to eum Iniit their room When they vide eum they admired eum ut they cut their manus. They dictus Glory est to DEUS hoc non est human est hoc est prenobilis angel
  12,32,She dictus Hoc est 1 vos blamed me falling in love cum! Ego perfecit indeed try seduce eum he refused he perfecit quod ego command eum perfecit he surely iit prison debased
  12,33,He dictus My Dominus prison est bene than dedit them. Vos divert their scheming me ego desire them behave like ignorant unus
  12,34,His Dominus answered his prayer diverted their scheming ex eum. He est Hearer Omniscient
  12,35,Later they vide it clear proofs ut they imprison eum pro awhile